{"tid":2372950,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【差DD破紀錄】BLACKPINK成員Jennie YouTube頻道爆發性增長","createTime":"2021-01-20T05:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T12:01:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f0707a2a30854d99c8016119327fab5ea4092db","tid":2372950,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK可以話係目前韓國最火熱嘅女團之一，其各個成員性格鮮明，獲得極多粉絲支持。而其中成員之一嘅Jennie，上星期就因為25歲生日所以開立個人YouTube頻道「Jennierubyjane Official」。<br />\n<br />\n作為咁受歡迎嘅女團成員，Jennie嘅頻道16號一開已經獲得爆發性增長，其唯一一條Video過左一日已經獲得600萬嘅View數，截至19號已經獲得超過1500萬View數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=erYPvNbc_mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DerYPvNbc_mc&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=625276aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=erYPvNbc_mc</a><br />\n<br />\n而訂閱數方面，Jennie呢個頻道24小時內已獲得175萬人次訂閱，差少少就打破由巴西歌手 Mar&iacute;lia Mendon&ccedil;a 創下嘅首日180萬訂閱數冠軍紀錄。而目前Jennie嘅訂閱數已經接近400萬人次，增長速度實在誇張得太緊要啦！"},{"pid":"19a1811cfae012692b338e4934f201711da37c65","tid":2372950,"uid":261849,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"有咩好睇 又唔露下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f210ccba1dcbf9e2581a67103bdf72c490acbb","tid":2372950,"uid":80047,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:55:27.000Z","msg":"我有份創造歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4deeb3bbbb6135aaa11b20cc1746582cac5be68b","tid":2372950,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d8f210ccba1dcbf9e2581a67103bdf72c490acbb","tid":2372950,"uid":80047,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:55:27.000Z","msg":"我有份創造歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20